            .</p>
               <p>Q. Will you look at the indorsement on that order, and tell me whose handwriting you believe it to be A. I cannot speak with certainty. If it is Mr. Taylor's handwriting it is counterfeited, and I can't tell.</p>
               <p>Q. If you had received that in an order on your bank, would you have cashed it - A. The middle line "Widow 
               <persName id="t18160110-59-person594">
